text: Wang Jianan may refer to: * Wang Jian'an (王建安; 1908–1980), Chinese general * Wang Jianan (table tennis) (born 1983), Congo table tennis player * Wang Jianan (footballer) (born 1993), Chinese footballer * Wang Jianan (long jumper) (born 1996), Chinese long jumper ==See also== * Wang Jian (disambiguation)
